Data format:

  data.py      - generic 3-d data container
  refldata.py  - definition of in-memory reflectometry data
  properties.py - date-tagged constants for varying instrument parameters

Nexus support:

  nxs.py       - NAPI wrapper
  nxsunit.py   - simple unit converter
  nxstest.py   - NAPI wrapper test
  nexus.py     - generic nexus file reader
  nexusref.py  - loader for NeXus refldata (not tested!)

ICP file support:

  icpformat.py - generic ICP reader
  ncnr_ng1.py  - instrument specific formats
  ncnr_ng7.py
 
Data transformations:

  correction.py - template and ideas
  anglecor.py   - angle correction
  normalize.py  - monitor normalization
  polcor.py     - polarization correction
  ratiocor.py   - estimate intensity from water measurement
  rebincor.py   - stub to wrap rebinning code (not implemented)
  reverse.py    - for reflectivity of the back of the sample
  err1d.py      - simple 1D error propagation
  wsolve.py     - weighted linear system solver

Application support:

  selection.py  - File selector

Plotting support:

  polplot.py    - 2-D polarized data plot
  polcorplot.py - polarization efficiency plot
  limits.py     - collect data limits

Matplotlib extensions
  canvas.py     - support for wx canvas
  binder.py     - support for objects on canvas
  ticker.py     - better log tic mark positions

